"Detailed setup, upgrade, and deployment instructions are available in the "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"Xehetasunezkoa ezarpena, eguneratze eta hedapen argibideak errepositorioan "
"eskuragarri daude."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:35
msgid "Manual Version Check"
msgstr "Bertsioa Eskuz Egiaztatu"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:36
msgid ""
"Run this command from the host to manually check for new Grylli releases:"
msgstr ""
"Exekutatu komando hau ostatik Grylli-ren bertsio berriak eskuz egiaztatzeko:"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Kudeatzaile Iradokizunak"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Ez exekutatu inoiz DEBUG gaituta ekoizpenean. Debug moduak xehetasun "
"barrukoak eta errore-trazak erakusten ditu."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Beti sakabanatu Grylli alderantzizko proxy baten atzean (adibidez, Caddy, "
"Nginx edo Traefik) eta zerbitza ezazu HTTPS bidez. Erabiltzaileen datu "
"sentikorrak bidean zifratuta egon behar dira."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr "Ziurtatu datu-karpeta (datubasea) zure ostatuan babesten dela"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
